### List Races
POST http://localhost:8000/v1/list-races
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "filter": {}
}

### List Races with Visible Only
POST http://localhost:8000/v1/list-races
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "filter": {
    "visible_only": true
  }
}

### List Races with Meeting ID
POST http://localhost:8000/v1/list-races
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "filter": {
    "meeting_ids": [1]
  }
}

### List Races with Default Sort (Advertised Start Time Ascending)
POST http://localhost:8000/v1/list-races
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "filter": {
    "sort_by": "SORT_BY_ADVERTISED_START_TIME",
    "sort_order": "SORT_ORDER_ASC"
  }
}

### List Races with Advertised Start Time Descending
